<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَالْمُسْلِمُونَ إِلَى الْمِيزَانِ قَدْ قُسِمُوا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>ثَلاثَةً فَاسْمَعُوا تَقْسِيمَ مُخْتَصِرِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَسَابِقٌ رَجَحَتْ مِيزَانُ طَاعَتِهِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَهُ الْخُلُودُ بِلا خَوْفٍ وَلا ذُعُرِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمُذْنِبٌ كَثُرَتْ آثَامُهُ فَلَهُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>شَفْعٌ بِأَوْزَارِهِ أَوْ عَفْوُ مُغْتَفِرِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَوَاحِدٌ قَدْ تَسَاوَتْ حَالَتَاهُ لَهُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>حَبْسٌ طَوِيلٌ وَبَيْنَ الْبِشْرِ وَالْحَصَرِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَيُكْرِمُ اللهُ مَثْوَاهُ بِجَنَّتِهِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>بِجُودِ فَضْلٍ عَمِيمٍ غَيْرِ مُنْحَصِرِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَفِي الطَّرِيقِ صِرَاطٌ مُدَّ فَوْقَ لَظَى<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>كَحَدٍّ سَيْفٍ سَطَا فِي دِقَّةِ الشَّعَرِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>النَّاسُ فِي وَرْدِهِ شَتَّى فَمُسْتَبَقٌ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>كَالْبَرْقِ وَالطَّيْرِ أَوْ كَالْخَيْلِ فِي النَّظَرِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>سَاعِي وَمَاشٍ وَمَخْدُشٍ وَمُعْتَلِقٍ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>نَاجٍ وَكَمْ سَاقِطٍ فِي النَّارِ مُنْتَشِرِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لِلْمُؤْمِنِينَ وُرُودٌ بَعْدَهُ صَدَرٌ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَالْكَافِرُونَ لَهُمْ وِرْدٌ بِلا صَدَرِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>فَيَشْفَعُ الْمُصْطَفَى وَالأَنْبِيَاءُ وَمَنْ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>يَخْتَارُهُ الْمَلِكُ الرَّحْمَنُ فِي زُمَرِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>